A massive convention hall viewed from above in vintage 1950s advertising illustration style, featuring thousands of tiny identical figures in business attire seated in perfect rows, all facing a distant elevated stage where a single small silhouette stands behind a podium, the scene rendered in muted teal, cream, and burnt orange tones with visible halftone dot patterns, geometric Art Deco ceiling panels creating dramatic perspective lines converging toward the stage, the crowd appearing almost like a sea of uniform dots, capturing the overwhelming scale and slight monotony of a corporate technology keynote event.
